Package com.rb.nonbiz.collections

Class IidPartition

java.lang.Object
com.rb.nonbiz.collections.IidPartition
All Implemented Interfaces:
PrintsInstruments
public class IidPartition
extends java.lang.Object
implements PrintsInstruments
Use this whenever you want to represent having N items with proportions that sum to 1, where the items all have a positive proportion.

Partition<T> is used all over the place. This is a specialized class similar to Partition<T>, which uses IidMap for better performance vs. a general RBMap. It was added relatively late, so it doesn't appear very frequently.
